2. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper involves speech recognition, which is a natural language processing task. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with video data and its effect on lip-reading, which falls under the domain of multimedia. 
4. cs.SD (Sound) - The paper involves speech recognition, which is related to sound processing.
